data.description: This charming single-story ranch home in Simi Valley offers a fantastic opportunity to own a stunning property with a beautiful backyard. As you enter, you are greeted by a bright and open floor plan that leads into a cozy living room complete with a fireplace. The heart of the home is the kitchen, which is truly a chef's dream. It features stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, and extra counter seating. Adjacent to the kitchen is a formal dining room, perfect for hosting dinner parties or family gatherings.  There is also extra space that can be transformed into an office or game area.  Hardwood floors add warmth and elegance to the main areas, while the double pane windows and sliding glass doors provide ample natural light and energy efficiency.  The bedrooms and baths in this home are spacious and comfortable.  The backyard is a true retreat, with a covered patio for BBQs, a corner gazebo, a swimming pool heated by owned solar panels, a beautiful tile patio, and fresh landscaping. It's the perfect space for outdoor entertaining or simply enjoying the California sunshine.  Conveniently located near schools, a park, a bike path, and essential shopping centers, this home offers both convenience and accessibility. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your dream home. Schedule a viewing today before it's gone!
